ildren":"As a specialized veterinary tool, we process patient data including medical histories, diagnostic imaging, lab results, pharmaceutical records, and provider notes. This information is treated with the same level of care as human medical records under HIPAA-equivalent standards."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"privacy-policy-group","children":[["$","h3",null,{"children":"Usage & Technical Data"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We collect diagnostic information required to ensure our platform operates with performance, including session duration, tool utilization metrics, IP addresses, and device identifiers to ensure platform stability and optimization."}]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"privacy-policy-section","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"3. How We Use Your Information"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"privacy-policy-intro","children":"We utilize collected data solely for the following professional purposes:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"privacy-policy-list","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Providing and maintaining the VETLIN Clinical platform services."}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Enabling secure collaboration among professional veterinary teams."}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Ensuring accurate authentication and professional verification."}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Generating analytics to improve diagnostic workflows and UX efficiency."}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Compliance with legal obligations and veterinary regulatory standards."}]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"privacy-policy-highlight","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"4. Data Sharing & Disclosure"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We do not sell clinical data. Data sharing is limited to functional clinical requirements:"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"privacy-policy-highlight-grid","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"children":"Instinct Integration"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"VetLink Clinical maintains a deep integration with Ins